title: Republican presidential candidates juggle day jobs, campaign
text: Republican presidential candidates juggle day jobs, campaign By Associated Press | October 20, 2015 @ 12:36 am FILE - In this Oct. 15, 2015 file photo, Republican presidential candidate, Ohio Gov. John Kasich speaks in Nashua, N.H. As Kasich travels the country in a quest for the presidency, his people back home want Ohioans to know that he's still focused on his day job and "his cellphone works just as well in Cincinnati, Iowa, as it works in Cincinnati, Ohio," as his spokesman put it. (AP Photo/Jim Cole, File)
